  "prompt": "How do I check my last 3 charges in Vodafone?",
  "response": "To check your last 3 charges on Vodafone, you can try the following methods:\n\n1. MyVodafone App:\n- Download and log into the MyVodafone app\n- Go to \"Bills\" or \"Usage\"\n- View recent charges and statements\n\n2. Online Account:\n- Visit the Vodafone website\n- Log into your online account\n- Check billing section for recent charges\n\n3. Call Customer Care:\n- Dial 198 from your Vodafone number\n- Speak to a customer service representative\n- Request information about recent charges\n\n4. SMS:\n- Send a specific SMS code to check balance and charges\n- Check with Vodafone for the exact SMS code\n\n5. Call *198#:\n- Dial *198# on your Vodafone mobile\n- Follow the menu options to check recent charges\n\nThe exact method might vary slightly depending on your specific Vodafone service and region, so it's best to confirm the precise steps with Vodafone customer support.",
